```
STOWAGE CONFIGURATION:
Units per Starship: 11,538
Stowage density: 0.15 units/m³
Total mass: 150,000 kg
Deployment mechanism: Rotary dispenser
Deployment rate: 100 units/minute
Deployment time: 2 hours per launch

LAUNCH MANIFEST:
Frequency: 2 launches/month
